<td style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em;font-weight:bold;border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Crystal_Clear_app_browser.png" class="image"><img alt="Portal icon" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Crystal_Clear_app_browser.png/16px-Crystal_Clear_app_browser.png" width="16" height="16" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Crystal_Clear_app_browser.png/24px-Crystal_Clear_app_browser.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fe/Crystal_Clear_app_browser.png/32px-Crystal_Clear_app_browser.png 2x" /></a> <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portal:Internet" title="Portal:Internet">Internet portal</a></td>
